title: Invest In the Future! Multi-Family Duplex 230 Cypress
text:
Invest In the Future! Multi-Family Duplex 230 Cypress ad date: 10/24/2015 
Multi-Family Duplex 230 Cypress Street, Brookings Well maintained with a good rental history. 2 units, each with 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths with great living space in each, glass slider to deck, fenced back yard and 2-car attached garage. Conveniently located to library, shopping and beach. Live in one, have parents in one unit with you next door or rent both for income. No. 13293675 $272,500 Sarah Pettinger
